<br>
I usually sit in Everfrost by the PoP book (re-casting MS to get an Ice Giant pet. &quot;help help, there is an ice giant in the newbie area!&quot;) to farm spiderling silk, and usually get several beggars.<br>
<br>
&quot;Can I have some Buffs and plat plz?&quot;<br>
&quot;Sure, bring be back a stack of Spiderling Silk or LQ/MQ/HQ pelts and I will buff you and pay you.&quot;<br>
&quot;How much?&quot;<br>
&quot;More than I should.&quot;<br>
<br>
Most just leave, but some say OK and come back with small amounts of silk and 2 or 3 hides.  I give them a sizeable donation (20pp usually), a good DS and a couple clicky lev rings, and tell them to give me a buzz if they ever get a horde of farming stuff.  I've still got one or two that give me tells and have become quite the little farmers.<br>
<br>
But if they aren't willing to work, they take a walk.  If they are rude, I will trick them into grouping and dispell any buffs they might have, or give them a summoned staff and show them how to dispell themselves.  That is always fun. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=alitaryoko>AlitaRyoko</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.geocities.co.jp/HeartLand-Sumire/7069/img/ddani.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Conjurer</span><br>  Posts: 212<br> <font color=#333333>(1/14/03 5:45 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8413.topic&index=45>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.co.jp/HeartLand-Sumire/7069/img/ddani.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: .</span><hr size=1> Hey Barm.  That's an excellent idea, putting the beggars to work. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    <p><A HREF=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=371031><center><img src="http://www.illumincathari.com/images/profile/maja_sig.jpg"></center> </A>
